00:20:08,356 --> 00:20:10,289
We don't have any leads,
but that won't stop us!

506
00:20:10,322 --> 00:20:13,289
[ Door opens, bell jingles ]

507
00:20:13,322 --> 00:20:14,389
-What's wrong?

508
00:20:14,422 --> 00:20:16,289
-Brother might know.
-What?

509
00:20:16,322 --> 00:20:18,656
-He might know
where Fuyumi is right now.

510
00:20:18,689 --> 00:20:20,089
-Huh?!

511
00:20:20,122 --> 00:20:22,856
-Because he put
a tracking device in her body.

512
00:20:22,889 --> 00:20:24,122
-When?!

513
00:20:24,156 --> 00:20:25,989
-When he took a sample
with that device.

514
00:20:26,022 --> 00:20:28,689
-Why did you wait
to tell me about this?!

515
00:20:28,722 --> 00:20:30,622
Because brother made me
swear to him

516
00:20:30,656 --> 00:20:32,689
that I would never tell this
to anybody.

517
00:20:32,722 --> 00:20:34,022
-That son of a --

518
00:20:34,056 --> 00:20:36,089
Then he knew
that this was gonna happen!

519
00:20:36,122 --> 00:20:38,289
So, was he the one
that abducted her?!

520
00:20:38,322 --> 00:20:41,289
-What?! No!
Brother would never do that!

521
00:20:42,956 --> 00:20:44,889
-I don't know
what he's up to exactly,

522
00:20:44,922 --> 00:20:47,189
but it's the only lead we've got
to work with.

523
00:20:48,856 --> 00:20:51,022
Take this and go back
to the Acropolis.

524
00:20:51,056 --> 00:20:53,322
Call me when you find out
where Fuyumi is.

525
00:20:53,356 --> 00:20:56,089
-No. I can't do that. He said
I couldn't come home yet.

526
00:20:56,122 --> 00:20:57,322
-Don't worry.

527
00:20:57,356 --> 00:20:59,222
If he says anything to you
at all,

528
00:20:59,256 --> 00:21:02,089
tell him I started going crazy
when Fuyumi went missing

529
00:21:02,122 --> 00:21:03,856
and I threatened you.

530
00:21:03,889 --> 00:21:05,622
You can have it all,

531
00:21:05,656 --> 00:21:08,322
everything I've ever collected
from the human world --

532
00:21:08,356 --> 00:21:10,389
the anime, manga, games, music.

533
00:21:10,422 --> 00:21:14,222
I'll hand over all of them
to you, okay?

534
00:21:14,256 --> 00:21:16,822
Just find Fuyumi for me.

535
00:21:16,856 --> 00:21:18,956
Please, Liz.

536
00:21:18,989 --> 00:21:20,222
-[ Sighs ]

537
00:21:20,256 --> 00:21:24,222
You...gave me <i>this.</i>

538
00:21:24,256 --> 00:21:27,022
He's enough.
That's all I want.

539
00:21:27,056 --> 00:21:29,622
-Are you sure that's it?

540
00:21:29,656 --> 00:21:31,189
-Yeah.

541
00:21:34,222 --> 00:21:37,356
Don't get me wrong --
I'm not doing this for <i>you.</i>

542
00:21:37,389 --> 00:21:42,189
Fuyumi's a bad girl,
but...she was kind of okay.

543
00:21:42,222 --> 00:21:43,756
-Is that right?

544
00:21:51,756 --> 00:21:53,822
-[ Grumbles ]

545
00:21:53,856 --> 00:21:57,389
-You better bring her back,
or I'll never forgive you.

546
00:22:01,756 --> 00:22:03,322
-Got to admit --
you're starting to become

547
00:22:03,356 --> 00:22:05,189
quite the little bad girl
yourself, Liz.

548
00:22:05,222 --> 00:22:07,122
[ Cellphone ringing ]

549
00:22:07,156 --> 00:22:08,289
-Got some info, boss.

550
00:22:08,322 --> 00:22:09,822
Earlier this morning,

551
00:22:09,856 --> 00:22:11,989
a stranger had his breakfast
at a diner here.

552
00:22:12,022 --> 00:22:14,122
-What'd he look like?
-Gimme a second.

553
00:22:14,156 --> 00:22:17,356
Mamejiro and Saty were able
to do a Search Eye on the place.

554
00:22:17,389 --> 00:22:19,322
Yoshida's
morphing into the guy now,

555
00:22:19,356 --> 00:22:20,822
so we'll send you a pic.

556
00:22:20,856 --> 00:22:22,022
-Good work, you guys.

557
00:22:22,056 --> 00:22:24,122
-That looks pretty close.
-Hmm.

558
00:22:24,156 --> 00:22:26,622
-This is the guy, boss.
You seen him before?

559
00:22:26,656 --> 00:22:28,356
-With clothes and hair
like that,

560
00:22:28,389 --> 00:22:31,722
he looks like a guy who'd be in
some kind of British boy band.

561
00:22:31,756 --> 00:22:32,989
Did you see which way he went?

562
00:22:33,022 --> 00:22:34,222
-Uh...

563
00:22:34,256 --> 00:22:36,322
-That way --
toward South Demon World!

564
00:22:36,356 --> 00:22:37,622
-Did you catch that?

565
00:22:37,656 --> 00:22:40,322
-Yeah, I heard.
Thanks.

566
00:22:40,356 --> 00:22:42,289
South, huh?

567
00:22:48,097 --> 00:22:52,097
-[ Singing in Japanese ]

568
00:24:17,964 --> 00:24:21,697
-It's not like I don't trust
what Liz says...

569
00:24:23,597 --> 00:24:26,130
...but nobody's
gonna take Fuyumi!

570
00:24:33,964 --> 00:24:36,530
-Give me my panties.

571
00:24:36,564 --> 00:24:38,897
-Sorry. I can't hear you.
-I said give me back my panties!

572
00:24:38,930 --> 00:24:40,197
-What?

573
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:42,130
-Those panties in your hand --
give them back!

574
00:24:42,164 --> 00:24:44,530
-Next time on "Blood Lad" --
"Two is a Treasure."

575
00:24:44,564 --> 00:24:48,064
-In the demon world,
it's good to be bad.

